    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a concours-level E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of atmospheric S54 engineering. This specimen features the iconic 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been fully overhauled for timing precision. The power is delivered through a tactile Getrag six-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring exceptional lateral grip. The chassis integrity is absolute, with a reinforced rear subframe and a suspension geometry that remains factory-spec. Finished in Carbon Black with a flawless Nappa leather interior, the vehicle exhibits no clear coat failure or bolster wear. Extensive documentation confirms that the rod bearings and cooling system have been refreshed, making this a mechanically superior example for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
